    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- build time:Wed May 15 2019 12:05:17 GMT+0800 (China Standard Time) --><h1 id="写在前面"><a href="#写在前面" class="headerlink" title="写在前面"></a>写在前面</h1><p>Archlinux首选还是sogou拼音吧，因为rime需要定制，目前不想去折腾它，只是我的arch不知怎地无法使用sogou拼音。</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h1><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S fcitx fcitx-im fcitx-rime fcitx-configtool</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="添加配置"><a href="#添加配置" class="headerlink" title="添加配置"></a>添加配置</h1><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim ~/.xprofile</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">export GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line">export QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line">export XMODIFIERS='@im=fcitx'</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启。</p><h1 id="添加拼音"><a href="#添加拼音" class="headerlink" title="添加拼音"></a>添加拼音</h1><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fcitx-configtool</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="data:image/png;base64," data-original="arch%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85fcitx-rime.assets/1555994542372.png" alt="1555994542372"></p><!-- rebuild by neat -->]]></content>
    
